{"tid":2444771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PTT：日本人搶購台灣鳳梨 製作「販售地圖」","createTime":"2021-03-13T05:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T08:58:06.000Z","uid":337052,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"741a09a8b00204419f8140cfeae5c709033d51ea","tid":2444771,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">台灣鳳梨在日本遍地開花的八卦</span></strong><br />\n時間Fri Mar 12 22:10:32 2021<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GdTWhzOl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGdTWhzOl.jpg&h=1862b97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乳提，這個台灣鳳梨地圖是個熱心的日本友人做的<br />\n<br />\n已徵得他同意<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/placelists/list/B33yhCDyTVSvbNJOvThoIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fplacelists%2Flist%2FB33yhCDyTVSvbNJOvThoIQ&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=537040c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/placelists/list/B33yhCDyTVSvbNJOvThoIQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">在更早之前日本只有東京的西友才買得到鳳梨</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">現在連青森、飛騨高山、四國這些地方都買得到台灣鳳梨了是怎樣</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zxrz7Jml.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZxrz7Jml.jpg&h=56feb6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名古屋也有了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M9W2UIJl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM9W2UIJl.jpg&h=c80a7212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女朋友幫忙切鳳梨，不過她好像不愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0UUUpRol.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0UUUpRol.jpg&h=48056a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得跟日本節目推波助瀾也有關係<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">當然最大功臣還是中國，感謝他們</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1615558235.A.758.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1615558235.A.758.html&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=2140a4e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1615558235.A.758.html</a>"},{"pid":"fd2b8f8c90b02f405d67a2857acd3ef0c26fd6da","tid":2444771,"uid":15730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"台日友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582dde6ffb63f4ce26797cede5cfb2f15a24ad8b","tid":2444771,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd2b8f8c90b02f405d67a2857acd3ef0c26fd6da","tid":2444771,"uid":15730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"台日友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5babb291647dc738fdcd77904a05d04fb7394bad","tid":2444771,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j-Z6LV975-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj-Z6LV975-U&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=a258becd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j-Z6LV975-U</a>"},{"pid":"4b9ab2515b87869a110d5456386018359c39124e","tid":2444771,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4h6M_jWvHDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4h6M_jWvHDk&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=5b332bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4h6M_jWvHDk</a>"},{"pid":"a4d62ee99c25bf41a9b153cf7597fa341dc82c6e","tid":2444771,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":